name: Banned In China 1.03
description: 4th of a Series of 100 works that can be used as virtual flags in various Ethereum and other blockchain world environments. Make a virtual statement and be proud of being banned in China, it's how freedom rings. I also developed it with a slight nod to the 90s 'Parental Advisory' sticker so feel free to stick it on your meta-building and be proud of resisting human oppression, wherever it may come from.
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
